00:09:45.813 --> 00:09:47.000
Kamu harus tetap hidup

00:09:47.759 --> 00:09:48.720
dan jadilah istriku.

00:09:50.519 --> 00:09:51.360
Kalau begitu, kau bisa membalasku.

